name: Cis-app
body:
### Welcome to CIS APP
iOS App for RVC CIS Division.

Test APP:

1) If interested in testing please install below app and email UDID
a. Install App to find UDID:
   https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/udid-tool/id377602501?mt=8
b. From UDID app enter below email and send:
   c.konkol@rockvalleycollege.edu
c. Wait for email from c.konkol@rockvalleycollege.edu before going to step 2.

2) Install & Test App
Download app to iPhone/iPad:
https://ota.io/orffgd

Items to test:
Does app open?
Can you navigate to pages?
Is screen layout easy to use?
What suggestions do you have on:
Text, layout, colors, videos, etc?

3) Post Feedback/Issues 
https://github.com/ioscourse/CIS-APP/issues
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
